# Charles Plucker Portfolio - AI Assistant Rules

## Project Overview

This is Charles Plucker's personal portfolio website - a "personal anchor on the web" that authentically represents who he is as a human and professional. The site helps potential employers and teams understand if they would be a good fit to work together.

**Core Philosophy:** Charles is "not for everyone, but if a good fit, a great fit" - evidenced by consistently long tenures and strong colleague testimonials.

