## Technical Stack & Patterns

### Core Technologies
- **Next.js 16** (Pages Router) - Static export for Cloudflare Pages
- **React 19** - Functional components only
- **TypeScript** - Strict mode enabled
- **CSS Modules** - Component-scoped styling

### Code Style

#### Components
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Functional component with TypeScript
interface MyComponentProps {
  title: string
  optional?: boolean
}

export default function MyComponent({ title, optional = false }: MyComponentProps) {
  return <div>{title}</div>
}
```

```typescript
// ❌ BAD: Class components, default exports at bottom
class MyComponent extends React.Component { }
```

#### Styling
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: CSS Modules import
import styles from './Component.module.css'

<div className={styles.container}>
```

```typescript
// ❌ BAD: Inline styles, styled-components, Tailwind
<div style={{ margin: '20px' }}>
```

#### File Organization
- Component files: `ComponentName.tsx`
- Style files: `ComponentName.module.css`
- Co-locate related files in `components/` directory
- Data files in `data/` (JSON format)

