## Image & Media Handling

### Images
- Use Next.js `<Image>` component with `unoptimized={true}` (required for static export)
- Feature cards use Patagonia trip photos (Torres Del Paine, Lago Grey, Mirador Britanico)
- Testimonials have individual photos in `/images/testimonials/`
- All images should maintain aspect ratio and use `objectFit: 'cover'` when needed

### Video
- Background video at `/videos/background.mp4` (16MB, intentionally high quality)
- Set `playbackRate = 0.5` for slow-motion effect
- Always include `autoPlay`, `loop`, `muted`, `playsInline` attributes

