## Component Patterns

### State Management
- Use React hooks (`useState`, `useEffect`, `useRef`)
- Keep state local to components
- No global state management needed for this site

### Navigation States
The Navigation component has three scroll states:
- `top`: At page top (< 50px scroll)
- `video`: Within hero video (< viewport height - 100px)
- `below`: Below hero section

### Responsive Patterns
- **Mobile-first**: Write base styles for mobile, enhance for desktop
- **Progressive enhancement**: Core content accessible on all devices
- **Touch-friendly**: Minimum 44px touch targets on mobile

